QWC Install Guide
=================

SYSTEM SETUP
------------

/etc/passwd: put www-data shell to /bin/bash

/etc/sudoers: add the following line to the file:

www-data ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/pkill, NOPASSWD: /usr/local/qate/bin/qate, NOPASSWD: /bin/kill, NOPASSWD: /bin/echo, NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/gdb, NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/screen, , NOPASSWD: /etc/init.d/qate

CRON ENTRIES: 

* * * * * php /usr/local/qate/admin/jobs/scheduler.php


NGINX:

Add:
fastcgi_send_timeout 400s;
fastcgi_read_timeout 400s;
to vh vhsot file

Add:
client_body_timeout 400s;
client_header_timeout 400s;

PHP-FPM:
php.ini: max_execution_time = 400

pool.d/www.conf:
pm.max_children = 15


INSTALL
-------

Just run the "install.sh" script located at the root of the project.


